resources.string:
"Audit refers to audits and audits. 
In order to prevent speculators from disrupting the daily operations of the platform. To protect the interests of normal users and allow the platform to operate stably for a long period of time, the system will review the user's deposits and withdrawals. 
1. The same user only performs one calculation; (Note: the account number, mobile phone number, and mobile device are the same, that is the same user) 
2. Deposit amount: refers to the amount of single deposit; 
3. Audit limit : The amount spent on the platform. For example: subscriptions, gifts, games, etc.; 
4. Withdrawal limit: Each withdrawal limit is calculated independently and compared with the consumption limit to determine the withdrawal limit."

"1. Before enabling automatic balance conversion, please manually convert the quota to the account balance;

2. The transfer-in ratio is: 1 gold coin/number of game coins of equivalent value;

3. The transfer ratio is: 1 game coin/the equivalent amount of gold coins."

"Reminder: 
Different rebates have different odds. Click on the rebate paytable to view the rebate odds;
The lower the rebate, the lower the odds. It is recommended that the rebate set for the lower level should not be too low;
 Agent report, betting details, transaction details to check the development of the agent;
The recommended lower level is also the type of agent, no matter how many levels have been developed, you can get rebates."

"1. The content of the ranking is updated every hour; 
 2. The daily ranking is the display of the ranking information of the day; 
 3. The weekly ranking is the display of the ranking information of the week, that is, this week to the current day; 
 4. The list is the display of the ranking information of the month, that is, from the 1st to the current day of the month;
 5. The God of Gamblers list will not be displayed for users who have participated in less than 100 lottery games."

